column2: SELECT idcase, timestamp - (SELECT MIN(timestamp) FROM event_log WHERE idcase = event_log.idcase) AS tempo_levaro FROM event_log WHERE activity IN ('fim da viagem', 'declaração rejeitada pelo funcionário', 'pagamento efetuado')
column3: select p.idcase, strftime('%s', p.timestamp) - strftime('%s', e.start_time) as 'Fim da viagem', strftime('%s', x.timestamp) - strftime('%s', e.start_time) as 'Declaração rejeitada pelo funcionário', strftime('%s', y.timestamp) - strftime('%s', e.start_time) as 'Pagamento efetuado' from event_log p inner join (select MIN(timestamp) as start_time, idcase FROM event_log GROUP by idcase) e on e.idcase = p.idcase and p.activity = 'Fim da viagem' left join event_log x on x.idcase=e.idcase and x.activity = 'Declaração rejeitada pelo funcionário'  left join event_log y on y.idcase=e.idcase and y.activity = 'Pagamento efetuado'

column3: select p.idcase, strftime('%s', p.timestamp) - strftime('%s', e.start_time) as 'Fim da viagem', strftime('%s', x.timestamp) - strftime('%s', e.start_time) as 'Declaração rejeitada pelo funcionário', strftime('%s', y.timestamp) - strftime('%s', e.start_time) as 'Pagamento efetuado', f.activity from event_log p inner join (select MIN(timestamp) as start_time, idcase FROM event_log GROUP by idcase) e on e.idcase = p.idcase and p.activity = 'Fim da viagem' left join event_log x on x.idcase=e.idcase and x.activity = 'Declaração rejeitada pelo funcionário' left join event_log y on y.idcase=e.idcase and y.activity = 'Pagamento efetuado' inner join (select MAX(timestamp) as end_time, activity, idcase FROM event_log WHERE activity='Fim da viagem' or activity= 'Declaração rejeitada pelo funcionário' or activity='Pagamento efetuado' GROUP by idcase) f on f.idcase=e.idcase

column3: select e1.activity, e1.resource, e1.idcase from event_log AS e1 inner join event_log AS e2 on e1.idcase = e2.idcase  WHERE e2.activity = 'Fim da viagem' and e1.timestamp > e2.timestamp

column2: SELECT e1.activity, e1.timestamp, e1.resource, e1.cost, e2.activity AS responsavel FROM event_log e1 JOIN event_log e2 ON e1.idcase = e2.idcase AND e2.activity = 'fim da viagem' WHERE e1.activity!= 'fim da viagem' AND e1.timestamp > (SELECT MAX(timestamp) FROM event_log WHERE activity = 'fim da viagem');

column2: SELECT CASE WHEN activity LIKE '%funcionário%' THEN 'Funcionário' WHEN activity LIKE '%supervisor%' THEN 'Supervisor' WHEN activity LIKE '%administração%' THEN 'Administração' WHEN activity LIKE '%pré-aprovador%' THEN 'Pré-aprovador' WHEN activity LIKE '%responsável pelo orçamento%' THEN 'Responsável pelo orçamento' WHEN activity LIKE '%diretor%' THEN 'Diretor' END AS grupo, COUNT(*) AS quantidade_de_casos FROM event_log GROUP BY grupo;
column3: select count(DISTINCT idcase), 'funcionário' as grupo from event_log WHERE activity like '%funcionário%'  UNION select count(DISTINCT idcase), 'supervisor' as grupo from event_log WHERE activity like '%supervisor%'  UNION select count(DISTINCT idcase), 'administração' as grupo from event_log WHERE activity like '%administração%'  UNION select count(DISTINCT idcase), 'pré-aprovador' as grupo from event_log WHERE activity like '%pré-aprovador%'  UNION select count(DISTINCT idcase), 'responsável pelo orçamento' as grupo from event_log WHERE activity like '%responsável pelo orçamento%'  UNION select count(DISTINCT idcase), 'diretor' as grupo from event_log WHERE activity like '%diretor%'

column2: SELECT (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM event_log WHERE activity LIKE '%funcionário%') AS funcionario, (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM event_log WHERE activity LIKE '%supervisor%') AS supervisor, (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM event_log WHERE activity LIKE '%administração%') AS administracao, (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM event_log WHERE activity LIKE '%pré-aprovador%') AS preaprovador, (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM event_log WHERE activity LIKE '%responsável pelo orçamento%') AS responsavel_orcamento, (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM event_log WHERE activity LIKE '%diretor%') AS diretor
column3: select count(DISTINCT idcase), 'funcionário' as grupo from event_log WHERE activity like '%funcionário%'  UNION select count(DISTINCT idcase), 'supervisor' as grupo from event_log WHERE activity like '%supervisor%'  UNION select count(DISTINCT idcase), 'administração' as grupo from event_log WHERE activity like '%administração%'  UNION select count(DISTINCT idcase), 'pré-aprovador' as grupo from event_log WHERE activity like '%pré-aprovador%'  UNION select count(DISTINCT idcase), 'responsável pelo orçamento' as grupo from event_log WHERE activity like '%responsável pelo orçamento%'  UNION select count(DISTINCT idcase), 'diretor' as grupo from event_log WHERE activity like '%diretor%'
